HEADWORD: Stoccado
<hw>Stoc*ca"do</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>estocade</ets>, fr. Sp. <ets>estocada</ets>, or It.
<ets>stoccata</ets>, from Sp. <ets>estoque</ets>, or It.
<ets>stocco</ets>, a rapier, fr. G. <ets>stock</ets> a stick. See
<er>Stock</er>.]</ety> <def>A stab; a thrust with a rapier.</def>
